abstract:

Machine learning can seem daunting to beginners, but Python makes it accessible to everyone. This talk introduces attendees to the core concepts of machine learning, the Python libraries commonly used, and a hands-on walkthrough of building a simple ML model. By the end of this session, attendees will feel confident taking their first steps into the exciting world of machine learning.
